<p begin="139900000t" end="253300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}黒い闇の中  そっと咲いてた</b></font></p>
<p begin="139900000t" end="253300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>黑暗中悄悄绽放</b></font></p>
<p begin="260000000t" end="365100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}初めての心  君はきっと知らない</b></font></p>
<p begin="260000000t" end="365100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>我最初的心意  你一定不曾知晓</b></font></p>
<p begin="372200000t" end="428900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}差し伸べてくれた手を</b></font></p>
<p begin="372200000t" end="428900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>伸向我的手</b></font></p>
<p begin="432700000t" end="489800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}掴めずにいるわたしは</b></font></p>
<p begin="432700000t" end="489800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>未能抓住的我</b></font></p>
<p begin="492700000t" end="549000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}あとすこし  もうすこし</b></font></p>
<p begin="492700000t" end="549000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>再有一点点  还有一点点</b></font></p>
<p begin="550700000t" end="610400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}君にもっと  もとめている</b></font></p>
<p begin="550700000t" end="610400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>就一定能  得到你更多</b></font></p>
<p begin="612900000t" end="690000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}それは  ひとすじのヒカリ</b></font></p>
<p begin="612900000t" end="690000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>那是我  唯一的光芒</b></font></p>
<p begin="710500000t" end="822600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W9" size="32"><b>{\an8}心の行方を  今はまだ知りたくない</b></font></p>
<p begin="710500000t" end="822600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正大标宋_GBK" size="32"><b>心向何方  现在还不愿去想</b></font></p>
<p begin="910700000t" end="950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33"><b>{\an8}<font size="45">历物语  历与石头</font></b></font></p>
<p begin="910700000t" end="950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="36"><b>{\an8}本字幕仅供交流试看之用，如您喜欢本作品，请支持购买正版。<br />若因私自散布传播造成法律及相关一切问题，华盟字幕社概不负责。</b></font></p>
<p begin="950700000t" end="980700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="36"><b>{\an8}翻译：痛爱的飞鱼；后期：snow。</b></font></p>
<p begin="965700000t" end="980700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45"><font size="45">四月</font></font></p>
<p begin="1030800000t" end="1050800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45"><font size="45">四月十一日</font></font></p>
<p begin="1055400000t" end="1071600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么？石头？</font></p>
<p begin="1074100000t" end="1090000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  石头</font></p>
<p begin="1092500000t" end="1105800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">石头怎么了？</font></p>
<p begin="1109600000t" end="1173400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也不应该说是石头  更准确地说应该是石像才对</font></p>
<p begin="1176300000t" end="1185900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">石像？</font></p>
<p begin="1187600000t" end="1213900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  倒也不是那种石像</font></p>
<p begin="1223500000t" end="1286390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我在想忍野先生的工作不就是收集这些故事吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1289400000t" end="1301000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这些故事？</font></p>
<p begin="1304400000t" end="1341900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">都市传说  街谈巷说  道听途说</font></p>
<p begin="1343600000t" end="1386500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是我就想学校里的「七大不可思议」也应该算在里面吧</font></p>
<p begin="1388600000t" end="1408200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「七大不可思议」？哎？</font></p>
<p begin="1411600000t" end="1460800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过  好像也没听说有哪个学生死在咱们校园里</font></p>
<p begin="1462500000t" end="1484600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个…你说什么来着？</font></p>
<p begin="1487500000t" end="1540000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不好意思羽川  刚才的话题有些太散  我没听懂</font></p>
<p begin="1542100000t" end="1566700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？那个…应该算是…</font></p>
<p begin="1578400000t" end="1591800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">关于石头的怪谈？</font></p>
<p begin="1651800000t" end="1706900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原来如此  不过这东西既不是石头也不算石像吧</font></p>
<p begin="1711000000t" end="1746500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">羽川  你说的就是这块石头吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1751100000t" end="1762300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  没错</font></p>
<p begin="1764800000t" end="1809500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们在春假的时候不是给忍野先生添了不少麻烦吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1809500000t" end="1852000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以我就想如果直江津高中学校里有什么怪谈的话</font></p>
<p begin="1852000000t" end="1897900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就把这些事情报告给忍野先生如何</font></p>
<p begin="1901600000t" end="1920800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不知道这能不能聊表谢意啊</font></p>
<p begin="1923700000t" end="1932100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原来如此</font></p>
<p begin="1935800000t" end="2020500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过  直江津高中的历史也不算悠久  所以也没什么怪谈流传</font></p>
<p begin="2025100000t" end="2055500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可有一件事我却一直很在意</font></p>
<p begin="2069300000t" end="2095200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你指的就是这块石头吗？</font></p>
<p begin="2098100000t" end="2126500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这应该说是石头呢  还是石像呢</font></p>
<p begin="2126500000t" end="2149800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  没错  就是这么回事</font></p>
<p begin="2155600000t" end="2180700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过以前这里是没有这个东西的</font></p>
<p begin="2186100000t" end="2239500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我刚入学的时候对整个校园做过一次调查</font></p>
<p begin="2243200000t" end="2266200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你为什么要做这种事？</font></p>
<p begin="2269100000t" end="2332500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">人总想知道接下来三年生活的学校究竟是什么样的嘛</font></p>
<p begin="2338700000t" end="2404600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说大约在两年前你进行调查的时候  这块石头还不在这里</font></p>
<p begin="2407100000t" end="2432600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是不是  石头是在的</font></p>
<p begin="2436800000t" end="2453400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在这儿不就没什么问题了吗？</font></p>
<p begin="2456400000t" end="2505200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但是当时并不是现召这个样子  虽然有石头但是没有这个祠堂</font></p>
<p begin="2520200000t" end="2547300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">供品和放供品的台子也没有</font></p>
<p begin="2552700000t" end="2609900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说在这两年的时间里  有人把这块石头装饰成了一个石像</font></p>
<p begin="2609900000t" end="2635700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并把它供在这里</font></p>
<p begin="2687800000t" end="2735800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这样  她觉得你应该喜欢这种故事所以让我把这件事告诉你</font></p>
<p begin="2741600000t" end="2763800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也算是羽川的谢礼吧</font></p>
<p begin="2770400000t" end="2801700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这也很难算是怪谈</font></p>
<p begin="2818800000t" end="2834700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过到是个好故事</font></p>
<p begin="2836700000t" end="2858800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">得好好记录下来才行</font></p>
<p begin="2863400000t" end="2882200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那你有什么想法吗？忍野</font></p>
<p begin="2897200000t" end="2937300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">两年前只不过是块石头</font></p>
<p begin="2937300000t" end="3005200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">两年后却成为了汇集许多学生信仰的类似于怪异的东西</font></p>
<p begin="3005200000t" end="3019400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">会有这种事情吗？</font></p>
<p begin="3036900000t" end="3067000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">物体变成怪异的事情也不算新鲜</font></p>
<p begin="3077400000t" end="3087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过</font></p>
<p begin="3091600000t" end="3137000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">究竟是因为是怪异才被人信仰  还是因为被人信仰才成为怪异</font></p>
<p begin="3137000000t" end="3153300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这一点就很难说了</font></p>
<p begin="3165400000t" end="3210900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}因为是怪异才被人信仰  还是因为会被人信仰才被叫做怪异？</font></p>
<p begin="3210900000t" end="3225000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是不是</font></p>
<p begin="3228400000t" end="3254700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是「因为会被人信仰才被叫做怪异」</font></p>
<p begin="3258400000t" end="3312200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为是怪异才被人信仰  还是因为曾被人信仰才成为怪异</font></p>
<p begin="3328100000t" end="3393100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  的确是有细微的不同  不过这种区别有必要特意纠正一下吗？</font></p>
<p begin="3395600000t" end="3410700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在这里就有必要了</font></p>
<p begin="3415200000t" end="3459400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过光听你这么说也不太好理解</font></p>
<p begin="3462400000t" end="3482800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木君  你能不能把它画出来？</font></p>
<p begin="3488200000t" end="3521600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}哎？老实说我不太会画画</font></p>
<p begin="3521600000t" end="3531600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="23"><b>{\an8}<font face="方正准圆_GBK"><font size="33">或许你会觉得很意外</font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="3534900000t" end="3567100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？好吧  差不多就行了</font></p>
<p begin="3573300000t" end="3582900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我知道了</font></p>
<p begin="3601300000t" end="3633000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？祠堂原来是这种形状的啊</font></p>
<p begin="3637100000t" end="3704300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  不过在我的印象里那个祭坛就好像只是个放供品的桌子</font></p>
<p begin="3707600000t" end="3762700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">祠堂的外形制作得也有些拙劣  就好像照着什么东西做出来的</font></p>
<p begin="3766400000t" end="3774800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="3777700000t" end="3839000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好像是哪里的寺庙  或者是路边的地藏菩萨  道祖神什么的</font></p>
<p begin="3839000000t" end="3847300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">具体我也不太清楚  不过总觉得那个祠堂的形状有些眼熟</font></p>
<p begin="3847300000t" end="3886100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">具体我也不太清楚  不过总觉得那个祠堂的形状有些眼熟</font></p>
<p begin="3890300000t" end="3947900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂喂  你既然知道这些杂学怎么不早说？</font></p>
<p begin="3951200000t" end="4001200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还是说你是为了显示自己博学而故意留了一手吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4004200000t" end="4035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  我之前只是隐约有一种感觉</font></p>
<p begin="4035000000t" end="4078000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">直到把它画出来的时候才突然有了这种想法</font></p>
<p begin="4084200000t" end="4112600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过具体是什么东西我也想不起来</font></p>
<p begin="4117600000t" end="4186400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">总觉得好像在哪儿见过  或者说有些特征感觉不像是第一次见</font></p>
<p begin="4189800000t" end="4211900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野  你知道这是什么东西吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4222300000t" end="4249800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  我也不能说知道</font></p>
<p begin="4253600000t" end="4261500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过</font></p>
<p begin="4309900000t" end="4339500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过什么啊？不要把话说到一半好不好？</font></p>
<p begin="4341200000t" end="4369900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果有什么线索的话就告诉我啊</font></p>
<p begin="4377400000t" end="4426200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哈哈  阿良良木君真是有精神  是不是遇到什么好事了？</font></p>
<p begin="4440400000t" end="4489600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  那阿良良木君  你就这么跟班长小妹说好了</font></p>
<p begin="4491700000t" end="4520100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她应该能理解这里的玄机</font></p>
<p begin="4524300000t" end="4553900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「先暂停对学校怪谈的调查</font></p>
<p begin="4553900000t" end="4595200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">接下来去查一查直江津高中的课程表比较好」</font></p>
<p begin="4613900000t" end="4653600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟学生的本分应该是学习才对</font></p>
<p begin="4673600000t" end="4681500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊！</font></p>
<p begin="4685700000t" end="4702400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">到底是怎么回事啊？</font></p>
<p begin="4710700000t" end="4756600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这次就算是我庸人自扰了</font></p>
<p begin="4759900000t" end="4805800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">羽川  加把劲啊  你应该可以解释得让我也明白才对</font></p>
<p begin="4813300000t" end="4835800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算你让我加把劲我也…</font></p>
<p begin="4852100000t" end="4878800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">关于直江津高中的课程表</font></p>
<p begin="4881700000t" end="4926700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一年级的时候不是有「艺术」这类可选内容的课程吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4930500000t" end="4958000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我当时选的是「美术」</font></p>
<p begin="4958000000t" end="4983500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">其他同学也有选「书法」和「手工」的</font></p>
<p begin="4989300000t" end="5051000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野先生那句话所暗示的应该是「手工」的课程表</font></p>
<p begin="5057300000t" end="5067300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「手工」？</font></p>
<p begin="5070200000t" end="5074800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯</font></p>
<p begin="5079800000t" end="5128200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那门课的课程表里有一节是类似于制作小屋的课程</font></p>
<p begin="5135700000t" end="5176200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">简单说那个祠堂就是在那门课上制作的小屋</font></p>
<p begin="5188700000t" end="5226590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而且  从那个祠堂的外观来看这应该是个失败作</font></p>
<p begin="5232100000t" end="5261700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">发生的事情差不多就是这样</font></p>
<p begin="5268300000t" end="5315900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">某个学生在艺术课上做了一个小屋然而却没做好</font></p>
<p begin="5319200000t" end="5370500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然失败  但那至少也是上课时制作的作品  老师就叫他把作品带回家</font></p>
<p begin="5377200000t" end="5393000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是就算带回家还是要把它丢掉</font></p>
<p begin="5393000000t" end="5413100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是就算带回家还是要把它丢掉</font></p>
<p begin="5413100000t" end="5418500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是就算带回家还是要把它丢掉</font></p>
<p begin="5418500000t" end="5454400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是他就打算把它偷偷地丢在学校  并向垃圾场走去</font></p>
<p begin="5458900000t" end="5490600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就在这时  他路过了花坛附近</font></p>
<p begin="5506100000t" end="5544000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  那个花坛旁边的确有个垃圾场</font></p>
<p begin="5547800000t" end="5577000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是他就看到了那块看头</font></p>
<p begin="5579900000t" end="5636600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他便想「如果把那块石头放在里面  这个失败作说不定也变得能看了」</font></p>
<p begin="5650400000t" end="5683300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并不是因为有了祠堂才让石头看起来像是石像</font></p>
<p begin="5688300000t" end="5716700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是因为有了石头才让木块看起来像是祠堂</font></p>
<p begin="5722100000t" end="5750900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样一来失败作就不再失败了</font></p>
<p begin="5758000000t" end="5780900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">反的  顺序颠倒了</font></p>
<p begin="5783000000t" end="5825100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  当然拙劣的外观没有任何变化</font></p>
<p begin="5825100000t" end="5889000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过至少从不得不扔掉的失败作变成了一个祠堂  成了一个真正的小屋</font></p>
<p begin="5889000000t" end="5920700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是那个学生就这样回去了</font></p>
<p begin="5924000000t" end="5973200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就这样  一个好像被人所信仰的石像就这样产生了</font></p>
<p begin="5973200000t" end="5978200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就这样  一个好像被人所信仰的石像就这样产生了</font></p>
<p begin="6012400000t" end="6049500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是轻松了不少  这也是多亏了阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="6052500000t" end="6070800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？多亏了我？</font></p>
<p begin="6074100000t" end="6131700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为是阿良良木同学向忍野先生说这个祠堂好像在哪儿见过</font></p>
<p begin="6131700000t" end="6153000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野先生对发现事情真相的</font></p>
<p begin="6160100000t" end="6191800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是因为见过那东西模仿的原型</font></p>
<p begin="6191800000t" end="6234300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是因为自己上课的时候也曾经做过才觉得眼熟</font></p>
<p begin="6237600000t" end="6299400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">既然阿良良木同学没选「美术」  就说明你选的也是「手工」</font></p>
<p begin="6322300000t" end="6361900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  没错  就是这么回事</font></p>
<p begin="6364900000t" end="6392000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样一来这件事也算是尘埃落定了</font></p>
<p begin="6421600000t" end="6452900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂！不可以在走廊里跑！</font></p>
<p begin="6470400000t" end="6500000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">接下来便是后日谈  或者说这次的结局</font></p>
<p begin="6527100000t" end="6590900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  不用说大家也知道这个祠堂就是两年前我在木工课上制作的</font></p>
<p begin="6590900000t" end="6639300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为没办法拿回家  最终放在了花坛旁边</font></p>
<p begin="6646800000t" end="6668900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我知道忍野为什么笑得那么诡异了</font></p>
<p begin="6675600000t" end="6704800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他一定是在忍着不让自己大笑出来</font></p>
<p begin="6711400000t" end="6759400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为是怪异讨被人信仰  还是因为曾被人信仰才成为怪异</font></p>
<p begin="6764400000t" end="6779800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野是这样说的</font></p>
<p begin="6789400000t" end="6849900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然是些零食  但这石头最终到了被人供奉的地步也依然是不变的事实</font></p>
<p begin="6856200000t" end="6912100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许是我无意间的一个行为让这块石头成为了怪异</font></p>
<p begin="6920000000t" end="6962500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许一块普通的石头就这样成了一座珍贵的石像</font></p>
<p begin="6962500000t" end="6994200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并且成了下可思议的怪异</font></p>
<p begin="7005500000t" end="7042600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许有一天  不可思议也会变成普通</font></p>
<p begin="7052600000t" end="7096000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这么一想  漫无目的地来学校上学也是一样的道理</font></p>
<p begin="7122700000t" end="7152300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我还是回教室再问问羽川吧</font></p>
<p begin="7159000000t" end="7203600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不理解日常生活可贵之处的我是不是应该算做一块木石？</font></p>
<p begin="7266600000t" end="7282000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？这块石头…</font></p>
<p begin="7307000000t" end="7318700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不就是块混凝土嘛</font></p>
<p begin="7525200000t" end="7580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将烦恼踢开  石头顺势滚落</font></p>
<p begin="7525200000t" end="7580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}悩み 蹴飛ばして石が転がってく</font></p>
<p begin="7581100000t" end="7638200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">稍加掩饰的  是四月的事情</font></p>
<p begin="7581100000t" end="7638200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}少し 誤魔化した あれは四月のこと</font></p>
<p begin="7638200000t" end="7692400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">曾经的我们都是好奇心旺盛的开朗孩子</font></p>
<p begin="7638200000t" end="7692400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}好奇心旺盛で 明るい子供でした</font></p>
<p begin="7692800000t" end="7752500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">在背后推着我们的是那一天开始的冒险</font></p>
<p begin="7692800000t" end="7752500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}背中押したのは あの日からの冒險</font></p>
<p begin="7752500000t" end="7809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">追寻着那些不出格的热度</font></p>
<p begin="7752500000t" end="7809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}はみ出せない熱を追いに行って</font></p>
<p begin="7810000000t" end="7863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">到处闲逛</font></p>
<p begin="7810000000t" end="7863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}道草をしよう</font></p>
<p begin="7882600000t" end="7939800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将重要的梦想放进箱子</font></p>
<p begin="7882600000t" end="7939800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}箱に乗せ 大切な夢</font></p>
<p begin="7939800000t" end="7996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">踩起脚踏板  将它带到远方</font></p>
<p begin="7939800000t" end="7996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}ペダル回し 遠くまで さぁ 持ち出そう</font></p>
<p begin="7996100000t" end="8049900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">传说中我们的未来</font></p>
<p begin="7996100000t" end="8049900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}噂した 僕の未来は</font></p>
<p begin="8050300000t" end="8087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">有着我们各自的模样</font></p>
<p begin="8050300000t" end="8087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}個々人の伸びる丈に</font></p>
<p begin="8087000000t" end="8129100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">怎么说也听不懂</font></p>
<p begin="8087000000t" end="8129100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}聞いてもわからない</font></p>
<p begin="8129500000t" end="8189200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">听不懂啊听不懂</font></p>
<p begin="8129500000t" end="8189200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}わからない わからない</font></p>
</div>
